# Request is region of interest that contains observable space (fringe regions)
# and the requested amount of samples (response may contain less).
# Response is a list of camera poses from which the ROI can be observed,
# together with a list of expected information gain for each camera pose.
# Information gain is measured as revealed space [m^3]

race_msgs/BoundingBox roi
int32 sample_size
---
geometry_msgs/PoseStamped[] camera_poses
float32[] information_gain
